rbanisierung 'von unten' zu beleuchten.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4a1970er Jahre. 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aItalienische Geschichte. 4aKonflikt. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aPolitik. 4aRom. 4aSoziale Bewegungen. 4aSozialgeschichte. 4aStadt. 4aUrban Studies. 4aZivilgesellschaft. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Italy.2bisacsh  a1970s.  aCity.  aCivil Society.  aConflict.  aCultural History.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aHistory.  aItalian History.  aPolitics.  aRome.  aSocial History.  aSocial Movements.  aUrban Studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2015z9783110438635oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839428955zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839428955423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839428955/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2015  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016